        "ggx2ow1Z237_text": "<p>“The mask helps me feel put together, even when I don’t wear makeup. It’s my go-to before events or long work days. I wish I found it sooner.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>—&nbsp;RACHEL M., 47</strong></p>",
